Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:53.40,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei Kiriyama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zero? What a weird name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it suits you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't that right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have a home.\NYou don't have a family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't go to school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have any friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See? There's no place for you in this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}TAKABASHI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The calm mind is the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is hot, huh?\NWe're not even in the rainy season yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.43,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}JS CHILDREN'S\NSHOGI TOURNAMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what am I saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a time like this and all I can do\Nis comment on the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}JS CHILDREN'S SHOGI TOURNAMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHILDREN'S SHOGI TOURNAMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are you eating properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You left so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumu and Kyouko are worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Next stop: Tsukishima. Tsukishima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}New Message: 1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Inbox\NHinata Kawamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}From: Hinata\NTitle: To Kiriyama\NGood work today!\NWe're having\Ncurry tonight,\Nso come over!!\NWe'll be waiting\NSee you! \(^o^)/\N*Hinata*
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}For: Hinata Kawamoto\NRe: To Kiriyama\NThank you for\Nthe invitation.\NHowever,\NI'm feeling\Nunder the weather\Ntoday, so I think\NI'll stay h...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}New Message Received
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Akari Kawamoto\NOh no, Rei\NWe're having curry,\Nbut we don't\Nhave any\Npickled vegetables!!\NCould you please\Nbuy some at the\Nconvenience store\Non your way over?\NEggs, too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SUMIYOSHI SHRINE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rei is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're tired. Dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, hurry up! I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, did you get ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:11:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bought ice cream, and pudding, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Ice cream!\N- Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hyay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hina, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milk pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ZOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, you bought all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make room for the ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}BLOOMPH
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll pay you back for it.\NThis must've been expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But sorry, I didn't know which one to get,\Nand ended up buying a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me is happy with this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. How did your match go, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akari said it was an important match\Nfor your club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- Sis, feed me! Please feed me!\N- Feed me, feed me! Hurry, hurry, hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I'm falling! I haven't had anything\Nbut water since yesterday!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, not when I'm holding the pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:12:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, feed the kitties!\NAnd please set the table!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, Rei said he won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So good! Nummy, nummy, nummy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Hina! You're putting curry\Non the altar as an offering?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I shouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, Mom and Grandma loved curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still, putting curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But they did really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose it's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo loves curry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Grandma, tonight's curry has pork in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone, shall we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put egg on Momo's plate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. I wonder\Nif you can finish a whole egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now our next story.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the 16th in Hibiya City, police found\Nthe body of Shizuo Unagawa in his home{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}bludgeoned to death by a blunt instrument.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His eldest son Tadashi,\Na second-year university student,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who had been reported missing,\Nwas arrested.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to the authorities,\NTadashi is suspected of murdering{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}his father by beating him\Nwith a hammer dozens of times in the head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Suspicion of beating his father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's unfortunate for Mr. Kouda.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His league entrance after all this time\Nwas riding on that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And to think his own son\Nwould beat him so easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although maybe he was satisfied after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}...with a hammer dozens of times\Nin the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, that's only if he was his real son.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every move...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...felt like I was punching\Nwith my bare hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:14:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's so vivid, it's like I can still feel\Nthe warmth of the skin that I hit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, what's wrong? Are you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Maybe you have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want something warm to drink? Like milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zoom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Emergency! I'll warm some up for you!\N- Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring medicine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right.\NYou don't have to eat everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you should eat a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, the boy's sleeping already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about rude. Ate and nodded off, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He laid down after he finished eating,\Nas if he passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How'd his match go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He won, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But he was pale when he got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And he only ate a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, can't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he couldn't get any sleep\Nlast night either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let him rest here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go back to the shop and sleep there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's bean roasting day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to lock up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Goodnight, Grandpa.\NWe'll help you stuff the pancakes tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, please do! Alright, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He left his glasses on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei Kiriyama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a small town by a big river{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is where I'll be living.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rank C-1, 5th dan. Seventeen years old.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Profession: pro shogi player.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:50.01,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei Kiriyama
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:54.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Town Along the River
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}STARE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Owl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}STARE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it can't be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A magnificent white owl wouldn't just\Nshow up at somebody's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And plus it's standing on the tatami mat floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a cat, aren't you? I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I'm gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ZOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Here!\N- Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}BED HEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please stir it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- E-Eggs too, please!\N- Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}BLUNT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I woke you up like I said I would.\NLet's go, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm getting up now, don't worry.\N- See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Sis woke me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...why did I fall back asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be late! But this is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I don't have time.\NBut one more bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're gonna have more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your lunch! It's a little big, but I pressed it\Ntogether tightly, so it should be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is a strange side dish as a whole,\Nbut it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}BA-BAAAAM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}GRASP
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have morning practice,\Nso I have to go! Take your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ehhh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, what about the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Please lock up when you leave!\NThank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second, if I have your key,\Nyou won't be able to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, we'll find a way in somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}BAAAAM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}GONG
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SILENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:25.48,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STARE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll try going...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the heck, Kiriyama?\NThat's a huge rice ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or a soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Hayashida.\N- You're lucky to have rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm broke until the end of the month,\Nso this is all I can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So Kiriyama, do you guys get paid monthly\Nfor your matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Or do you get paid right after each match?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Monthly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They make bank deposits at the\Nend of the month for all matches played.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I've been following you online.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You've been on a winning streak,\Nso you must have a lot of matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, the Kiryuu Tournament, the Jeweled\NGeneral Tournament, the Rookie Tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Kiriyama.\NI don't want to think about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...is your monthly income more than mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}CHOMPALICIOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm not going to eat lunch with you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What?! Actually, I never asked you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If you don't like it,\Nhurry up and make friends here at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm an adult, so I'm really busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he became a professional during\Nmiddle school and considered a genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here, he's just a 17-year-old\Nwith issues like anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he's thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}MIKAZUKI-DOU
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rei! Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was the rice ball good?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing.\NCan you help us with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tie the ribbons on,\Nso could you put six in a box, and stack them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be a great help.\NGo ahead and wash your hands first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}EGG / CHUNKY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three each of egg bean paste\Nand chunky bean paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}CELEBRATION
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cute wrapping paper, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not printed, right? It looks expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Hina made it. Surprising, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's potato print.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I carved up sweet potatoes\Nand stamped them on. Cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're for Grandpa's calligraphy teacher friend,\Nwho's celebrating his 70th birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The big 7-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:17.48,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Spirited Away"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}All right. Who did this one, I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He taught Hina for a little while\Nwhen she was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is her present to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Hahaha, I suspected it was you, Hina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someji is very fortunate to have\Ngrandchildren who are willing to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Someji is a lucky fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The little one tags along annoyingly,\Nand she's so loud I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, look! I folded it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! Origami, huh?\NYou're so clever, Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sorry. Grandpa is a bit of a softie\Nwhen it comes to his grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Just a bit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off to deliver all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I'm staying for the party,\Nso take care of everything else. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}MIKAZUKI-DOU
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rei, you'll eat dinner with us tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you. But I'll be going home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have another...\Nanother match, so I'd better practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh?\N- You have a lot of matches. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, thank you for the rice ball.\NIt was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then here. Our baked "Crescent Moon."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just out of the oven, so it's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come over anytime! We'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Goodnight!\N- Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It still hasn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is this what you're looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...Rei Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:54.41,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rei Kiriyama\NMATCH NOTIFICATION
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:54.41,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHUB
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CRISP
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:00.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:34.30,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.30,0:24:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.30,0:24:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama prefers cup noodles\Nover the food Hina and I cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.27,0:24:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put me off like that, Kiriyama!\NWe're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.48,0:24:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.02,0:24:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Hanaoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.44,0:24:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.11,0:24:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"March Comes in Like a Lion."\NDon't miss the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.12,0:24:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
